					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Downvoted because you can just read the last tab and it works just fine. Also I'm not fully convinced about the effect - the hallucinatory part seems a bit much. Or, maybe not much, just&#8230; off&#8230; Why did the artist intend for that to happen? Isn't it cheating if you anomalously make your art stick to people's brains. I think that could be expanded. I mean, I did like the character and the interview.</p> <p>Oh, the corporate sheet has a typo. It says &quot;corpEration&quot;.</p> 
				 	]]>
